%vlocity_namespace%__PropertySet__c.text: Note: PPO plans — Prudent Buyer PPO and Select PPO network plans can only be offered alongside other plans with the same network type. (For example, plans on the Select PPO network can be offered alongside other plans on the Select PPO network, but they cannot be offered alongside plans on the Prudent Buyer PPO network. Not all network options are available in every area.) HMO plans — CaliforniaCare HMO and Select HMO network plans can only be offered alongside other plans with the same network type. (For example, plans on the Select HMO network can be offered alongside other plans on the Select HMO network, but they cannot be offered alongside plans on the CaliforniaCare HMO network. Not all network options are available in every area.
